OL,3,C'Nobody cared': Soldier's
OL,4,Cdisappearance not spotted for two weeks
OL,6,FThe parents of a soldier missing for
OL,7,Fthree months say "nobody cared" about
OL,8,Fhis disappearance after the Army took
OL,9,Ftwo weeks to report his absence.
OL,11,FL Cpl Ryan Rudd, of 1st Battalion
OL,12,FYorkshire Regiment, was on a night out
OL,13,Fwith two friends in Selby when he went
OL,14,Fmissing in the early hours of Sunday
OL,15,F15 February.
OL,17,FThe 28-year-old failed to return to
OL,18,Fhis base at Catterick Garrison in
OL,19,FNorth Yorkshire and has been out of
OL,20,Fcontact since.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
