FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779538271
OL,3,C'Nobody cared': Soldier's
OL,4,Cdisappearance not spotted for two weeks
OL,6,FHis parents Ken and Kerstin Rudd say
OL,7,Fthey were only informed two weeks
OL,8,Fafter he was last seen.
OL,10,FMrs Rudd said: "Nobody had noticed he
OL,11,Fwas missing. Nobody cared that he was
OL,12,Fmissing.
OL,14,F"Everybody knows that the first 24-48
OL,15,Fhours are the most important in a
OL,16,Fmissing person investigation, in any
OL,17,Fsort of police investigation. And the
OL,18,Fpolice had absolutely nothing to go
OL,19,Fon."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779538271
OL,3,C'Nobody cared': Soldier's
OL,4,Cdisappearance not spotted for two weeks
OL,6,FShe added: "There's no evidence, lots
OL,7,Fof the CCTV has been wiped - they only
OL,8,Fkeep it for a week. So they didn't
OL,9,Fhave a leg to stand on in finding
OL,10,Fwhat's happened to him."
OL,12,F"It put the police two weeks straight
OL,13,Fbehind." Mr Rudd added.
OL,15,FMrs Rudd described their son as the
OL,16,F"light" of their lives, a "happy-go-
OL,17,Flucky normal lad".
OL,19,F"Our lives haven't moved since we
OL,20,Ffound out," she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779538271
OL,3,C'Nobody cared': Soldier's
OL,4,Cdisappearance not spotted for two weeks
OL,6,F"We're still stuck in February. What
OL,7,Fis there to look forward to?"
OL,9,FMr Rudd added: "It was a highlight
OL,10,Fwhen he used to come home for leave. I
OL,11,Fused to look forward to it so much."
OL,13,FThe couple said the Army had told them
OL,14,Fa roll call is carried out at
OL,15,FCatterick each Monday to check if
OL,16,Fsoldiers have returned from weekend
OL,17,Fleave, but that officials had assumed
OL,18,FL Cpl Rudd was on a course.
OL,20,FIt is understood an investigation is
OL,21,Fnow being carried out into the delay.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
