FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779538271
OL,3,C'Nobody cared': Soldier's
OL,4,Cdisappearance not spotted for two weeks
OL,6,FNorth Yorkshire Police have previously
OL,7,Fsaid they are open minded about what
OL,8,Fhad happened to L Cpl Rudd, but it was
OL,9,Flikely he had entered the River Ouse.
OL,11,FL Cpl Rudd is described as white,
OL,12,Faround 5ft 8ins tall and slim, with
OL,13,Fdark brown hair.
OL,15,FIn a statement, an Army spokesperson
OL,16,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with Lance
OL,17,FCorporal Rudd's family and friends at
OL,18,Fthis difficult time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
