CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779538271
OL,3,C'Nobody cared': Soldier's
OL,4,Cdisappearance not spotted for two weeks
OL,6,F"While we continue to support North
OL,7,FYorkshire Police's investigation, it
OL,8,Fwould be inappropriate to comment
OL,9,Ffurther."
